text: Joshua Tuaniga (born ) is an American volleyball player, a member of the United States men's national volleyball team and Polish club Ślepsk Suwałki, PlusLiga. He competed for USA U19 team at the 2015 FIVB U19 World Championship and U21 team at the 2017 FIVB U21 World Championship. ==Sporting achievements== ===College=== * National championships ** 2018 16px NCAA National Championship, with Long Beach State Beach ** 2019 16px NCAA National Championship, with Long Beach State Beach ===National team=== * 2014 16px NORCECA U19 Championship * 2016 16px NORCECA U21 Championship * 2019 16px FIVB World Cup ===Individually=== * 2016: NORCECA U21 Championship – Most Valuable Player * 2016: NORCECA U21 Championship – Best Setter * 2018: NCAA National Championship – All-Tournament Team (Most Outstanding Player) * 2019: NCAA National Championship – All-Tournament Team ==External links== * Player profile at TeamUSA.org * Player profile at PlusLiga.pl * Player profile at Volleybox.net * Long Beach State Beach 2019 roster – Joshua Tuaniga * 2019 FIVB World Cup – Team USA * 2017 FIVB U21 World Championship – Team USA ==References== Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Long Beach, California Category:American men's volleyball players Category:American expatriate sportspeople in Poland Category:Expatriate volleyball players in Poland Category:Long Beach State Beach men's volleyball players Category:Ślepsk Suwałki players
